    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Builds automáticos com MSBuild, NUnit e NCover]]></title>
    <link href="http://vintem.github.io/templecoding/blog/2010/06/14/builds-automticos-com-msbuild-nunit-e-ncover/"/>
